OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FUp to 20 companies and 57 individuals
OL,7,Fcould face criminal charges over the
OL,8,FGrenfell fire, police and prosecutors
OL,9,Fhave said.
OL,11,FDecisions will be made on whether any
OL,12,Fcharges will be brought before the
OL,13,F10th anniversary of the disaster next
OL,14,Fsummer, the Metropolitan Police
OL,15,Fconfirmed.
OL,17,FPotential offences under consideration
OL,18,Finclude corporate gross negligence
OL,19,Fmanslaughter, fraud, health and safety
OL,20,Fbreaches, and misconduct in public
OL,21,Foffice.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/15
