OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779274977
OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FIn an update at New Scotland Yard on
OL,7,FTuesday, the Met Police said that
OL,8,Ffiles of evidence will be submitted to
OL,9,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service (CPS) by
OL,10,FSeptember 30 this year, with charging
OL,11,Fdecisions before June 14 2027.
OL,13,FSo far, 15 out of 20 files have been
OL,14,Fpassed to the CPS for advice.
OL,16,FBereaved relatives and survivors met
OL,17,Fthe news with "caution, grief and
OL,18,Fdetermination", saying they have
OL,19,Falready faced an unacceptably long
OL,20,Fwait for justice.
OL,26,@yD@OOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/15
