OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FPolice said 165 million electronic
OL,7,Ffiles had been gathered and searched
OL,8,Ffor evidence while 14,400 statements
OL,9,Fhave been taken during the mammoth
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
