OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FThe Met has looked at the role of
OL,7,F15,000 individuals and 700
OL,8,Forganisations relevant to the
OL,9,Finvestigation in what is the largest
OL,10,Fand most complex inquiry the force has
OL,11,Fever carried out.
OL,13,FThe blaze in June 2017 claimed the
OL,14,Flives of 72 people and was found by a
OL,15,Fpublic inquiry to have been avoidable.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
