PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779274977
OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FFrank Ferguson, from the CPS, said he
OL,7,Fis confident charging decisions will
OL,8,Fbe made before the 10th anniversary of
OL,9,Fthe fire, adding: "We do not
OL,10,Funderestimate the impact that such a
OL,11,Flengthy investigation has had and
OL,12,Fcontinues to have on the bereaved,
OL,13,Fsurvivors and the residents."
OL,15,FHe said it is difficult to see any
OL,16,Fcourt cases taking place before 2029,
OL,17,Fbut that the court service is aware of
OL,18,Fthe need to make potential contingency
OL,19,Fplans.
OL,26,@qD@SOUuD@]O]
