OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FBelow: Local Labour MP for Kensington
OL,7,Fand Bayswater Joe Powell told ITV News
OL,8,FLondon the wait had been 'agonising' -
OL,9,Fbut 'we have a chance to see people
OL,10,Fheld criminally accountable'.
OL,12,FInvestigators are building scale
OL,13,Freplica parts of the tower at a cost
OL,14,Fof #2 million in anticipation of
OL,15,Fpotential court proceedings.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
