CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779274977
OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FSpeaking at New Scotland Yard, the
OL,7,Fofficer in overall command of the
OL,8,Finvestigation Garry Moncrieff, who has
OL,9,Fstayed with the investigation despite
OL,10,Fretiring as a police officer, set out
OL,11,Fthe scale of the probe.
OL,13,FHe said forensic investigators spent
OL,14,F14 months at the tower itself
OL,15,Fgathering evidence, and have sifted
OL,16,Fthrough information linked to hundreds
OL,17,Fof companies and thousands of
OL,18,Findividuals, as well as going through
OL,19,Fdetails from the public inquiry.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779274977
OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,F"It is important that we do it once
OL,7,Fand do it right," he said.
OL,9,FWhile Mr Moncrieff would not be drawn
OL,10,Fon whether he feels there should be
OL,11,Fcharges brought, he said: "What I can
OL,12,Fsay is that we have gathered strong
OL,13,Fevidence and that evidence is
OL,14,Fsufficient that we will be submitting
OL,15,Ffiles to the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,16,Ffor them to make charging decisions."
OL,18,FHe added that while the public inquiry
OL,19,Fhad "slowed us down slightly", it had
OL,20,Fnot "held back anything we've done".
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@QO]sD@[OUxD@eO]{D@EOU{D@]O]|D@
OL,26,AEOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
