OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779274977
OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FHe described the Met update as "a
OL,7,Freally significant day" for families,
OL,8,Fwhile acknowledging it had taken "a
OL,9,Flong time to get here".
OL,11,FHe added: "It's really important that
OL,12,Fwe do it in the most professional and
OL,13,Fdiligent investigation possible to
OL,14,Fenable that justice is done."
OL,16,FA spokesman for Grenfell United, which
OL,17,Frepresents some of the families
OL,18,Fbereaved by the disaster and
OL,19,Fsurvivors, insisted there must be no
OL,20,Ffurther delay.
OL,26,@nD@`OUoD@WO]pD@bOUqD@VO]sD@KOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
