CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779274977
OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FThe group said: "Today's update from
OL,7,Fthe Metropolitan Police marks an
OL,8,Fimportant step in a process that has
OL,9,Falready taken far too long.
OL,11,F"Nearly 10 years after the Grenfell
OL,12,FTower fire claimed the lives of 72
OL,13,Fpeople, bereaved families, survivors
OL,14,Fand residents are being told that
OL,15,Ffiles will begin to be passed to the
OL,16,FCrown Prosecution Service in September
OL,17,F2026, with charging decisions expected
OL,18,Fbefore the 10th anniversary.
OL,26,@nD@QOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779274977
OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,F"For our community, this is not news
OL,7,Fwe meet with celebration. We meet it
OL,8,Fwith caution, grief and determination.
OL,9,FWe have waited almost a decade for
OL,10,Faccountability.
OL,12,F"No family should have to wait over 10
OL,13,Fyears for justice for their loved
OL,14,Fones, if it comes at all.
OL,16,F"The final report of the Grenfell
OL,17,FInquiry laid bare the shocking
OL,18,Ffailures, dishonesty and disregard for
OL,19,Fhuman life that led to the fire.
OL,20,FGrenfell was not a tragedy without
OL,21,Fcause.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779274977
OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,F"Those responsible must now be held to
OL,7,Faccount.
OL,9,F"But after waiting nearly 10 years,
OL,10,Four community cannot be expected to
OL,11,Fendure years more of delay.
OL,13,F"The Ministry of Justice and the
OL,14,FGovernment must ensure the courts are
OL,15,Fproperly resourced so that any
OL,16,Fprosecutions linked to Grenfell are
OL,17,Fheard swiftly.
OL,19,F"Justice delayed any further would be
OL,20,Funacceptable."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
