CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779274977
OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FThe Grenfell Inquiry found that the
OL,7,Fdisaster was preceded by "decades of
OL,8,Ffailure" by governments and the
OL,9,Fbuilding industry to act on the
OL,10,Fdangers of flammable materials on high-
OL,11,Frise buildings.
OL,13,FIt also found victims, the bereaved
OL,14,Fand survivors were "badly failed"
OL,15,Fthrough incompetence, dishonesty and
OL,16,Fgreed.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@HO]vD@TOUvD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779274977
OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FThe tower block was covered in
OL,7,Fcombustible products because of the
OL,8,F"systematic dishonesty" of firms which
OL,9,Fmade and sold the cladding and
OL,10,Finsulation, inquiry chairman Sir
OL,11,FMartin Moore-Bick said in his final
OL,12,Freport in 2024.
OL,14,FHe also condemned the "deliberate and
OL,15,Fsustained" manipulation of fire safety
OL,16,Ftesting, misrepresentation of test
OL,17,Fdata and misleading of the market.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@WO]vD@WOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
