OL,3,CDozens of people and 20 firms could be
OL,4,Ccharged over Grenfell fire
OL,6,FSo far, the police investigation into
OL,7,Fthe fire has cost #150 million, with a
OL,8,Fteam of 220 officers and staff working
OL,9,Fon the inquiry, and a specialist team
OL,10,Fof 20 staff at the Crown Prosecution
OL,11,FService.
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/15
